#

Pumpkin and Spinach Salad

30 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

NutsDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuick

Description

A refreshing salad featuring roasted pumpkin and fresh spinach, topped with a zesty dressing.

Ingredients

  • pumpkin: 2 cups, cubed
  • fresh spinach: 4 cups
  • feta cheese: 1/2 cup, crumbled
  • walnuts: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • honey: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
